# ObserveAI Stage 1.6 тАФ Event Architecture Redesign for AI Automation

## Analysis of Real V2 Export JSON

### What the V2 data actually contains (72 events parsed)

```
Apps observed: Launcher, Settings, Reddit, RedBus, Gboard
Time window: ~3 minutes (1782111514 тЖТ 1782111697)
```

**App breakdown:**
| App | Events | Issues |
|-----|--------|--------|
| `com.android.launcher` | 31 events | 99% noise тАФ `VIEW_FOCUSED` on FrameLayout, no meaning |
| `com.android.settings` | 9 events | OK but `screenTitle:"OFF"` is wrong (button label leaking into screenTitle) |
| `com.reddit.frontpage` | 11 events | Best data тАФ typing captured correctly, but fieldLabel pollutes later events |
| `com.google.android.inputmethod.latin` | 8 events | Pure noise тАФ IME window state changes carry zero value |
| `in.redbus.android` | 3 events | `fieldLabel:"Any update on ace results?"` leaking from Reddit тАФ critical bug |

