### Component 1 тАФ FocusStateTracker (NEW FILE)

Extracted from `ObserveAccessibilityService` into its own class. Per-package state, automatically cleared when the active package changes.

```kotlin
class FocusStateTracker {
    private var activePackage: String? = null
    var focusedFieldHint: String? = null
        private set
    var focusedFieldLabel: String? = null
        private set

    fun onPackageChanged(newPackage: String) {
        if (newPackage != activePackage) {
            activePackage = newPackage
            focusedFieldHint = null   // тЖР clears context leakage
            focusedFieldLabel = null
        }
    }

    fun onFieldFocused(hint: String?, label: String?) {
        focusedFieldHint = hint
        focusedFieldLabel = label
    }

    fun clear() { focusedFieldHint = null; focusedFieldLabel = null }
}
```

---

### Component 2 тАФ ScreenSnapshot (NEW)

For `WINDOW_STATE_CHANGED`, walk the active window's view tree and collect:
- All non-empty text nodes (up to 20, to cap CPU cost)
- All clickable elements (text + resourceId)
- All editable fields (hint + current value)

```kotlin
data class ScreenSnapshot(
    val screenTexts: List<String>,           // All visible text
    val clickableElements: List<ClickableElement>,
    val editableFields: List<EditableField>
)

data class ClickableElement(val text: String, val resourceId: String?)
data class EditableField(val hint: String?, val value: String?)
```

---

### Component 3 тАФ SessionTracker (NEW FILE)

A session = a continuous sequence of events within the same app (or app group) without a gap > 30 seconds.

```kotlin
class SessionTracker {
    private var currentSessionId: String = UUID.randomUUID().toString()
    private var lastEventTimestamp: Long = 0
    private var lastPackage: String = ""
    private val SESSION_GAP_MS = 30_000L

    fun getSessionId(packageName: String, timestamp: Long): String {
        val gap = timestamp - lastEventTimestamp
        val appChanged = packageName != lastPackage
        if (gap > SESSION_GAP_MS || (appChanged && gap > 5000)) {
            currentSessionId = UUID.randomUUID().toString()
        }
        lastEventTimestamp = timestamp
        lastPackage = packageName
        return currentSessionId
    }
}
```

