## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Q1: Screen snapshot scope** тАФ Should we snapshot every `WINDOW_STATE_CHANGED` (may include Settings, notifications) or only whitelisted apps (RedBus, Uber, Zomato)? Whitelisting reduces noise and CPU cost.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Q2: `fieldLabel` vs `fieldHint`** тАФ Should we drop `fieldLabel` entirely and only keep `fieldHint`? The V2 data shows `fieldLabel` is always wrong (it reflects current text value, not the field's label). I recommend dropping it and using only `fieldHint` + `contentDescription`.

> [!NOTE]
> **Q3: Text-change strategy** тАФ Currently we emit one event per debounce window. A better approach: capture the **final** value only on `VIEW_FOCUSED` leaving the field (detected via focus moving to another field). Should we implement this?

